{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6878092af3","title":"关于一九六七年文化大革命的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"23e6e82edc","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":1,"articleId":"6878092af3"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6530f9ab78","type":"title","text":"关于一九六七年文化大革命的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3"},{"id":"89b611090a","type":"paragraph","text":"1.今年搞文化大革命的指导思想是《红旗》和《人民日报》元旦社论，展开全面的阶级斗争。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3"},{"id":"cc165524ab","type":"paragraph","text":"2.要抓四个重点。北京、上海、天津、东北。责任是在造反派身上，要团结多数，造反派队伍要超过一倍以上。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3"},{"id":"8dab79ccdc","type":"paragraph","text":"3.上海很有希望，许多学生、工人、机关干部起来了，这是当前文化大革命的形势。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3"},{"id":"7f7d307b56","type":"paragraph","text":"4.红卫兵要向解放军学习，一定要朴素","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3"},{"id":"766c1e8866","type":"paragraph","text":"祝你们明年过社会主义关！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3"}],"page":{"id":"5b35edc5bd","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3","start":258,"end":258}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"35350d27e5","type":"paragraph","text":"3．上海很有希望，许多学生、工人、机关干部起来了，这是当前文化大革命的形势。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6878092af3"},{"id":"4af3bf1bd1","type":"title","text":"关于一九六七年文化大革命的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6878092af3"},{"id":"99e4457db5","type":"paragraph","text":"1．今年搞文化大革命的指导思想是《红旗》和《人民日报》元旦社论，展开全面的阶级斗争。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6878092af3"},{"id":"a6e8b42f4e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席在元旦祝酒时说：“祝你们明年过社会主义关！”","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6878092af3"},{"id":"b001aa662b","type":"paragraph","text":"4．红卫兵要向解放军学习，一定要朴素。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6878092af3"},{"id":"ba6b2cf67b","type":"paragraph","text":"2。要抓四个重点。北京、上海、天津、东北。责任是在造反派身上，要团结多数，造反派队伍要超过一倍以上。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6878092af3"},{"id":"fb6bfa2d63","type":"paragraph","text":"（张春桥同志传达）","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6878092af3"}],"page":{"id":"95de24d12d","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6878092af3","start":543,"end":543}}}},"__N_SSG":true}